/><br />\n<br />\n1. 我會加入/所屬於一個為我的團體爭取政治和法律權利的組織。<br />\n2. 我會捐錢給一個為我的團體爭取政治和法律權利的組織。<br />\n3. 我會義務幫一個為我的團體爭取政治和法律權利的組織工作（例如寫請願信，分發傳單，招募人員等）。<br />\n4. 我願意蹣跚行走一個小時參加一次公開集會、抗議或示威，以支持我的團隊。"},{"pid":"e35ef0eed7738d6d4f4732b521e0c49877fbf061","tid":2176830,"uid":28763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:02:52.000Z","msg":"咁難明既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da235d44ee0fc9669be1c21959e9a3c40b72847b","tid":2176830,"uid":173598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6857e39217716388e2acbd9b39ad5110e5514cc9","tid":2176830,"uid":90601,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T10:27:38.000Z","msg":"都仲有4成中立撚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:04:28.000Z","msg":"4成花生撚"},{"pid":"3ac41936b90b09d0f782d5d10fd31b6f8ca91ef7","tid":2176830,"uid":168389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"da235d44ee0fc9669be1c21959e9a3c40b72847b","tid":2176830,"uid":173598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6857e39217716388e2acbd9b39ad5110e5514cc9","tid":2176830,"uid":90601,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T10:27:38.000Z","msg":"都仲有4成中立撚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:04:28.000Z","msg":"4成花生撚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:08:28.000Z","msg":"仲有狗畜生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}